snippet.textDisplay: Why the fuck would you build an incredible custom pc to surprise a millionaire. Nothing against the pc, it's amazing, but what is the point of making it for someone who has enough money to commission it from some fabricator one ten times over, a drop in the bucket. Again the computer is amazing but, I am disappointed in LTT for doing it for a celebrity millionaire, it just seems like a move to garner millions of views and not to generously blow a less privileged persons mind. It seems to me an utter waste for them to build this for someone who can easily already afford custom PC's and flagship component performance.
